# PWA & Offline

## Requirements

- App must work offline after first successful online load
- Persist user progress and preferences in IndexedDB (Dexie preferred)
- Document cache/version strategy when changing SW precache list

## Storage

- Schema version field on stored records
- Reset checklist must clear both UI state and persisted completion flags
- Avoid localStorage for large or structured checklist state

## Testing

Verify manually: airplane mode, reload, iOS Add to Home Screen when possible.

See `agents/pwa-offline-agent.md` for full checklist.
